WEBVTT

00:09:41.386 --> 00:09:44.481
We would sit down together
and talk about our work.

00:09:45.187 --> 00:09:46.862
I would try to explain

00:09:46.886 --> 00:09:48.044
(Laughter)

00:09:48.068 --> 00:09:50.990
how and why I did them,

00:09:51.014 --> 00:09:54.164
the meaning, the feeling,
why they were relevant.

00:09:55.490 --> 00:09:58.855
Mom, on the other hand,
would just bluntly say,

00:09:58.879 --> 00:10:00.053
"sì,"